gear_list.Name: d&b audiotechnik J12
gear_list.Comment: J12 loudspeaker The J12 is a 3-way design housing 2 x 12' LF drivers, one hornloaded 10' MF driver and two 1.4' exit HF compression drivers with 3' voicecoils mounted to a dedicated waveshaping device. The mechanical and acoustical design enables flown vertical columns of up to 24 loudspeakers to be suspended using vertical splay angles between them of 0° to 7° with a 1° resolution

gear_list.Name: db audiotechnik. D80
gear_list.Comment: The 2 RU four channel D80 amplifier is a high power density amplifier, ideally suited for use in both mobile and installation environments. It contains configurations for all d&b loudspeakers and a linear mode
